task.summary:
`displayStacktrace` option has now 4 modes available #26
* all: display stacktraces for failed specs and in failures summary. * specs: display stacktraces for failed specs only. * summary: display stacktraces in failures summary only. * none: do not display stacktraces.

Rework documentation
- Use syntax highlighting - Use relative links for page & image
Tests: Use jasmine env instead of fake env #25
Special case for top level suite
Disabled specs was incorrectly reported as failed #28
Fixes All specs displayed when using fdescribe and fit. #37
Fixes All specs displayed when using fdescribe and fit. #37
Ensure that colors are always enabled. #36.
Have same sign/color convention than jasmine default reporter for pending specs
Add pending summary to display pending reasons. #33

Bump jasmine version to 2.4.1
Update test for https://github.com/jasmine/jasmine/pull/942
